<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.10.6">
<l>tuppa ṉaitturaṅ kampaṭac cīṟiya tōṉṟa laiccuṭar vāṉkalaṉ peytatōr</l>
<l>ceppi ṉaitiru maṅkaima ṇāḷaṉait tēva ṉaittika ḻumpava ḷattoḷi</l>
<l>yoppa ṉaiyula kēḻiṉai yūḻiyai yāḻi yēntiya kaiyaṉai yantaṇar</l>
<l>kaṟpi ṉaikaḻu nīrmala rumvayal kaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw for myself in Kaṇṇamaṅkai, with fields where dark lilies flower,</l>
<l>The mighty [lord], the phenomenon that split the horse to kill [it],</l>
<l rend="indent">a chest that scatters abundant jewels that sparkle,</l>
<l>Bridegroom of lady Tiru, god, the one with the brilliant gloss</l>
<l rend="indent">of coral that shines, the seven worlds,</l>
<l>The eons, the one with the hand that bears a discus,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the scholarship of priests.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
